snippet.title: Johnny Depp LOSES libel case against The Sun over Amber Heard ‘wife-beater' claims
snippet.description:
Subscribe to the Evening Standard on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7RQon_YwCnp_LbPtEwW65w?sub_confirmation=1

Johnny Depp’s Hollywood career lay in tatters today as a High Court judge ruled he was violent abuser of wife Amber Heard during their tumultuous marriage.  

The Pirates of the Caribbean star, 57, played a high-stakes gamble when he sued The Sun for libel over a 2018 article branding him a “wife beater”.  

Depp and his expensively-assembled legal team called out actress Heard as a liar, branding the domestic abuse claims a “hoax” and insisting she had concocted a #MeToo story during their five-year romance.  

But in a blockbuster showdown this summer, Aquaman star Heard revealed how Depp had punched her in the face, repeatedly throttled her, dragged her around by her hair, and pelted her with bottles.  

Read more: https://www.standard.co.uk/news/uk/johnny-depp-amber-heard-libel-case-result-sun-b39887.html
